text: Novoturayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Beketovsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 269 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 47 km from Yermekeyevo, 22 km from Beketovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Novoturayevo
